==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bidding prayer
<hw>Bid"ding prayer`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(R. C.
Ch.)</fld> <def>The prayer for the souls of benefactors, said before the
sermon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Angl. Ch.)</fld> <def>The prayer before the sermon,
with petitions for various specified classes of persons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Biddy</ent>⟦br⟧
